[30;1m42 | [0m[35m        key = f"AWS4{self.secret_key}".encode()[0m
[30;1m43 | [0m[35m        key = hmac.new(key, timestamp[0:8].encode("utf-8"), sha256).digest()[0m
[30;1m44 | [0m[35m        key = hmac.new(key, self.region.encode("utf-8"), sha256).digest()[0m
[30;1m45 | [0m[35m        key = hmac.new(key, b"sts", sha256).digest()[0m

[30;1m11 | [0m[35m    instead of sys/init. This API completes in 2 phases. Once this is invoked, the joining node[0m
[30;1m12 | [0m[35m    will receive a challenge from the Raft's leader node. This challenge can be answered by the[0m
[30;1m13 | [0m[35m    joining node only after a successful unseal. Hence, the joining node should be unsealed using[0m
[30;1m14 | [0m[35m    the unseal keys of the Raft's leader node.[0m
[30;1m15 | [0m[35m[0m
